info.headline: Wind Advisory issued December 29 at 1:47AM PST until December 29 at 7:00PM PST by NWS Monterey
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 PM PST THIS EVENING... * WHAT...South winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 45 mph expected. * WHERE...Portions of California. * WHEN...From 7 AM this morning to 7 PM PST this evening. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
